Package jsgrewal.conwaysapi

Interface MemoryDataStructureInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataStructure
    public interface MemoryDataStructureInterface
    Title: The Memory Data Structure Interface

    Description: This interface contains various methods related to storing and retrieving the state of live or dead cells in the Conway's Game of Life.

    Author:
    LRCarter, Jaskirat

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      long getDataStructureHeight()
      Getter for Data Structure Height
      long getDataStructureSize()
      Getter for Size Occupied by Data Structure
      long getDataStructureWidth()
      Getter for Data Structure Width
      boolean readDataStructure​(long row, long col)
      This routine will take row index and column index as parameters and tell if the cell is alive or not.
      void writeDataStructure​(long row, long col, boolean isAlive)
      This routine will take row index, column index and boolean signifier (cell is alive or dead) and insert it to the data-structure.

    • Method Detail

      • readDataStructure

        boolean readDataStructure​(long row,
                          long col)
        This routine will take row index and column index as parameters and tell if the cell is alive or not.
        Parameters:
        row - The Row Index
        col - The Col Index
        Returns:
        True if cell is Alive and False if cell is dead

      • writeDataStructure

        void writeDataStructure​(long row,
                        long col,
                        boolean isAlive)
        This routine will take row index, column index and boolean signifier (cell is alive or dead) and insert it to the data-structure.
        Parameters:
        row - The row index
        col - The col index
        isAlive - True (Alive) or False (Dead)
